    {
      "id": "result",
      "durationMs": 37500,
      "narration": {
        "text": "Some issuers receive a prebuilt extension from an SDK vendor. The generic iOS app-extension mechanism (ios/app_extensions// in your project) covers that path, and this release improves it: it now works without CocoaPods, and each extension can carry its own provisioning profile, either as a file in its folder or through a per-extension hint."
      },
